
This assignment is due at 11:59pm on Thursday, April 21. Four total late days are available to you for
this course. One point will be deducted for each unexcused late day. Homework submissions will not be
accepted after 11:59pm on Thursday, April 29.

Description
• Implement a tree with an arbitrary number of children.
• Write a method serialize, which writes the tree to a text file, and deserialize, which reads a tree
from a text file.
• Implement the other methods required by main.
• Test your tree with main.

Submission

In Blackboard, submit

• Your Ntree.h
• Any other related files.

Make sure your code has your name in a comment at the beginning of each file.